								<foliation>
									<p>127 folios (+ 2 paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>20 quires (nos. 1-18, 20-21), originally of 10 leaves each.</p>
									<p>Apart from the quires 3, 13, 18, all the quires are imperfect.</p>
									<p>The quires are signed with Hebrew letters and Arabic numerals on the upper margin of the first page.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Lacunae after folios: 1, 2, 3, 9, 19, 20, 23, 27, 28, 32, 33, 36, 37, 45, 49, 50, 51, 57, 59, 72, 73, 75, 79, 81, 89, 98, 108.</p>
									<p>Many folios stained or water-damaged.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="16" writtenLines="16">
									<p>Uniform layout.</p>
									<p>The numbers of the chapters have been added by a later hand.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
